  <summary date="2025-07-16T10:29:03Z" status="Introduced in House">Defund NPR Act

This bill prohibits federal funding of National Public Radio (NPR) or any successor organization.&#160;The prohibition includes the payment of dues to or the purchase of programming from NPR by a public broadcast station using federal funds.</summary>
